            <thetext>Currently, it is not possible to store additional data while building a form. Such additional data may be a description text, a help text, ... which could be required by the custom form renderer to render the needed information. The basic idea is to add and store a data map with every added form element which will be available for the renderer on render time.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
